{"id":369,"slug":"rpj-role-playing-james","url":"https://www.brightonfringe.org/events/rpj-role-playing-james/","title":"Rpj Role Playing James","company":"James Bennison","genre":"Comedy","description":"Step into a world of wild imagination, chaos and comedy. Under the guidance of ex-comedian and self-proclaimed “James-Master” James Bennison, audience members are plucked at random and thrust into the spotlight as the heroes of a totally improvised fantasy adventure. Armed only with enthusiasm (and maybe a grenade), they must battle bizarre creatures, solve ridiculous riddles, and roll gigantic dice, all while James desperately tries to keep the story on the rails. Whether you’re a seasoned role-player or have never touched a character sheet in your life, this show invites you to join a roaring quest where everything is made up and no two nights are ever the same. Expect epic triumphs, catastrophic failures, and the kind of heroic nonsense that can only come from comedy colliding with high fantasy. If you love laughter, adventure and glorious unpredictability join the party. Your destiny awaits, whether you want it or not.","duration_minutes":60,"age_suitability":"18+","image_url":"https://content.brightonfringe.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/11-28-2025-121451-7336.jpg","website":"","instagram":"https://www.instagram.com/brightonfringe/","twitter":"https://twitter.com/brightonfringe","facebook":"https://www.facebook.com/brightonfringefestival","accessibility_features":["Assistance Dog"],"content_warnings":["Violence"],"cast":[],"scraped_at":"2026-05-19T15:10:07.168766","venue":{"id":2,"slug":"laughing-horse-the-walrus-hideaway","name":"Laughing Horse @ The Walrus (Hideaway)","address":"10 Ship Street, East Sussex","url":"https://www.brightonfringe.org/venues/laughing-horse-the-walrus-hideaway","lat":50.8216908,"lng":-0.1421673},"performances":[{"id":31989,"date":"2026-05-31","time":"","standard_price":null,"concession_price":null,"is_sold_out":false,"booking_url":""